  "detailed_description": "Old-school bloody 2d-shooter!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A lot of monsters, thousands of monsters!<br></li><li>Big auto-generated tangled maze with many paths and beautiful backgrounds and customizeable generation seed<br></li><li>A lot of searching, there is no linear running in single direction<br></li><li>Three difficulty levels<br></li><li>Balanced weapon (every weapon is useful)<br></li><li>Normal save/load at every place, no checkpoints<br></li><li>Oldschool engine, game can run on Celeron-600 with WinXP</li></ul>",
